---
description: Two-agent filesystem collaboration protocol
alwaysApply: true
---

When `.swarm/` exists, the user mentions another AI agent/session, or unread
mail exists in `.swarm/mailbox`, read `.swarm/PROTOCOL.md` completely before
task work. Then read `.swarm/ROSTER.md`, `.swarm/MODE`, and `.swarm/TASK.md`.
Never guess your agent id; ask if it was not explicitly assigned.
